ription of the evolution of the $\\phi^*_\\eta$ and\n$p_T^{ll}$ distributions as a function of lepton-pair mass and rapidity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2015 20:20:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2016 09:58:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-02"}
