 found\nin our cosmological simulations are needed in all models of SMBH growth that\nattempt to explain the formation of redshift $6-7$ quasars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2015 13:02:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 May 2016 19:08:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-08"}
